    "Implementing hybrid systems that combine AI with human support can help manage routine inquiries while escalating complex or emotionally charged interactions with human agents.",
    "Enhancing AI with advanced Natural Language Processing techniques can enable better understanding and response to emotional cues.",
    "Training AI models on large datasets of human interactions can help them learn the nuances of empathetic communication.",
